name beamertheme-tcolorbox
category Package
revision 77380
shortdesc A beamer/ltx-talk inner theme to reproduce standard beamer blocks using tcolorboxes
longdesc This package provides an inner theme for beamer or ltx-talk
longdesc which reproduces standard beamer blocks using tcolorboxes. The
longdesc look and feel (rounded/sharp corners, shadows and colours) will
longdesc automatically adapt to which other themes are loaded.
depend beamer
depend tcolorbox
depend tikzfill
depend tools
